        "timestamp": "2020-05-29 14:32:36.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAll,\n\nThis is the first change built off of the VES 7.2 spec.  It is moving NF requirements out of the spec.  I've also taken the opportunity to organize the sections a bit more logically. For example, there were sections in the front about concepts like event ID even before the concept of the Common Header had been introduced.\n\nThis is a fairly large commit, and I know we have other changes we want to make.  Please try to prioritize your review of this if at all possible so we can get this in, and minimize conflicts with future changes.\n\nThanks,\nTrevor",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
