        "timestamp": "2020-06-01 14:53:05.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(7 comments)\n\nOverall, the documents look good.\nI noticed a few smaller thing, but overall, the doc looks good so far.\nOn the SNMP collector topic - probably a Data File Collector (DFC) would be a better example.",
