        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-06-01 16:07:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI am not aware of the background of this commit. I see this commit has removed many requirements in 7.4 monitoring & management. Are those requirements removed permanently or moved to somewhere else(e.g the equivalent requirements are covered in VES event listener)?",
