        "timestamp": "2020-06-02 14:41:18.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> I am not aware of the background of this commit. I see this commit has removed many requirements in 7.4 monitoring & management. Are those requirements removed permanently or moved to somewhere else(e.g the equivalent requirements are covered in VES event listener)?\n\n\nDepends on the the requirement in question.  Some were moved within the document, some were never supported, and others were redundant.  If there are particular ones of concern please let me know which ones, and we can discuss on the VES call or via email.",
        "patchset_number": 1
