        "timestamp": "2020-06-02 14:44:43.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI think I've addressed all comments except for 3 areas I need confirmation\n\n1) Confirmation of SNMP Collector support (full vs. traps only) - Damian\n2) Confirmation of where to change SNMP to DFC - Damian\n3) Clarification on which removed requirements are of concern - Junfeng\n\nWe can address as much as we can on the weekly call, and I'll track down the rest offline.\n\nThanks,\nTrevor",
